  <p>The exact home price that matches each budget depends on rate, down payment, term, tax, and insurance. That is why affordability should be modeled with a mortgage calculator, not guessed from price alone.</p>

  <h2>Common Mistakes Buyers Make</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Using the lender maximum instead of a comfortable budget</li>
    <li>Ignoring property tax, insurance, HOA, or PMI</li>
    <li>Choosing a payment that leaves no room for repairs or cash reserves</li>
    <li>Assuming a low teaser rate or perfect refinance scenario</li>
    <li>Forgetting moving costs, furniture, closing costs, and maintenance</li>
  </ul>

